1. *Hriste* je bilo puno ljudi na proslavi. (There were a lot of people at the celebration.)

2. On je živeo u starom *hristu*. (He lived in an old manor.)

3. Volim da trčim u *hristu*. (I like to run in the meadow.)

4. On je otišao u *hristu* da traži lekovito bilje. (He went to the meadow to search for medicinal herbs.)

5. Mi smo se igrali u *hristu* dok je sunce sijalo. (We were playing in the meadow while the sun was shining.)